indicator("Swing Structure Forecast [BOSWaves]", overlay = true)

// Swing detection using highest/lowest over swingLen bars
// Tracks swing highs/lows, creates S/R zones, forecasts next swing target
// BUY when swing low confirmed (dir flips to uptrend)
// SELL when swing high confirmed (dir flips to downtrend)
